Dodge::Engine Entity Placement Tool

- In the XML editor, write the XML code defining some game asset.
- Click add to toolbox
- Assets of that type may then be added to the map
   - When added, the asset joins the list of added game assets.
   - To position the asset, click the 'pos' xml node in the xml editor, and click the map.
   - Its compoundPoly is set similarly.
   - We only want to store the XML that differs from the asset's definition/prototype
      - Click the 'reduce' button. This happens automatically when the map is saved/exported.
